      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S0120-PRIVS-RTN.
      *
           MOVE  "S0120"                    TO   BSGEROR-PARA
      *
      *    COPY  DBIOPRIV.
      *
      * Z-M-U-0000(F/W ON-LINE)
      * Z-B-D-0000(F/W BATCH)
      *
           IF   DBIO-CALL-PGM-ID(1:1)       =   "Z"
           THEN
                GO TO S0120-PRIVS-EXT
           END-IF
      *
      * A-FA-0000(ON-LINE)
      * B-FA-0000(BATCH)
      *
           MOVE  DBIO-CALL-PGM-ID(2:2)      TO   WORK-APPL-ID
      *
           MOVE  CONT-PROGRAM-ID(2:2)       TO   WORK-DBIO-ID
      *
           IF  WORK-APPL-ID      = WORK-DBIO-ID
           THEN
               GO TO S0120-PRIVS-EXT
           ELSE
               MOVE  CONT-SYSERROR          TO   DBIO-STAT
      *{E} DBIO모듈에서 에러종료 되었습니다.
               MOVE  "S9000020"             TO   XZUGEROR-I-ERRCD
               MOVE  "UKLA0002"             TO   XZUGEROR-I-TREAT-CD
               MOVE  SPACE                  TO   XZUGEROR-I-MSG
               STRING  "("
                       WORK-APPL-ID
                       ")업무는 ("
                       WORK-DBIO-ID
                       ")DBIO를 사용할 권한이 없습니다"
                                                 DELIMITED BY SIZE
                     INTO  XZUGEROR-I-MSG
               PERFORM  S9100-ERROR-END-RTN
                  THRU  S9100-ERROR-END-EXT
           END-IF
           .
       S0120-PRIVS-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *  수행조건 : DBIOCA를통해받은DBIO-키를각가의해당키로MOVE
      *  처리기능 : DBIO-ACCESS-KEY에따라분기하여KEYVALUE를MOVE
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S0130-KEYVALUE-MOVE-RTN.
      *
           MOVE  "S0130"                    TO   BSGEROR-PARA
      *
           INITIALIZE                            KEY-DB-TABLE
      *
           MOVE  DBIO-ACCESS-COND           TO   WORK-ACCESS-COND
      *
           IF  COND-DBIO-FETCH   OR  COND-DBIO-CLOSE
           THEN
               GO TO S0130-KEYVALUE-MOVE-EXT
           END-IF
      *
           IF  COND-DBIO-INSERT  OR  COND-DBIO-LKUPDT
           THEN
           MOVE  GROUP-CO-CD  OF  DBIO-RECORD
             TO  GROUP-CO-CDP0 OF KEY-DB-TABLE
           MOVE  BASE-YM  OF  DBIO-RECORD
             TO  BASE-YMP0 OF KEY-DB-TABLE
           MOVE  ONCP-DSTCD  OF  DBIO-RECORD
             TO  ONCP-DSTCDP0 OF KEY-DB-TABLE

           MOVE  PK-THKJL0049               TO   DBIO-KEY


           IF  GROUP-CO-CD OF DBIO-RECORD NOT = "KB0"
           THEN
               MOVE  CONT-SYSERROR  TO   DBIO-STAT
               MOVE  "S9000099"     TO   XZUGEROR-I-ERRCD
               MOVE  "UKLA0002"     TO   XZUGEROR-I-TREAT-CD
               MOVE   9901          TO   XZUGEROR-I-LINE
               MOVE
                     "그룹회사코드를 'KB0' 로 사용하세요!!!"
                                    TO   XZUGEROR-I-MSG
               PERFORM  S9100-ERROR-END-RTN
                  THRU  S9100-ERROR-END-EXT
           END-IF

           END-IF
      *
           EVALUATE  TRUE
               WHEN  COND-DBIO-PK
                     MOVE  DBIO-KEY         TO
                                            PK-THKJL0049
                     MOVE  GROUP-CO-CDP0 OF KEY-DB-TABLE
                       TO  GROUP-CO-CD  OF  DBIO-RECORD
                     MOVE  BASE-YMP0 OF KEY-DB-TABLE
                       TO  BASE-YM  OF  DBIO-RECORD
                     MOVE  ONCP-DSTCDP0 OF KEY-DB-TABLE
                       TO  ONCP-DSTCD  OF  DBIO-RECORD
           END-EVALUATE
           .
       S0130-KEYVALUE-MOVE-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *  수행조건 : DBIOCA를통해받은DBIO-키중접근조건범위에해
      *             필드의 값을 찾아서 MOVE
      *  처리기능 : DBIO-ACCESS-KEY에따라 KEY VALUE를 MOVE
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S0140-KEYVALUE-DISP-RTN.
      *
           MOVE  "S0140"                    TO   BSGEROR-PARA
      *
           IF  COMM-DB-II-OUTPT-DSTCD       =    "1" OR "9"
           THEN
               CONTINUE
           ELSE
               GO TO S0140-KEYVALUE-DISP-EXT
           END-IF
      *
           IF  COND-DBIO-FETCH   OR  COND-DBIO-CLOSE
           THEN
               GO TO S0140-KEYVALUE-DISP-EXT
           END-IF
      *
           EVALUATE  TRUE
               WHEN  COND-DBIO-PK
                     MOVE  "PK:그룹회사코드                ="
                                            TO BSGDISP-TEXT(1:34)
                     MOVE  GROUP-CO-CDP0 OF KEY-DB-TABLE
                                            TO BSGDISP-TEXT(35:)
                     PERFORM  S7700-BSGDISP-RTN
                        THRU  S7700-BSGDISP-EXT
                     MOVE  "PK:기준년월                    ="
                                            TO BSGDISP-TEXT(1:34)
                     MOVE  BASE-YMP0 OF KEY-DB-TABLE
                                            TO BSGDISP-TEXT(35:)
                     PERFORM  S7700-BSGDISP-RTN
                        THRU  S7700-BSGDISP-EXT
                     MOVE  "PK:자기자본구분                ="
                                            TO BSGDISP-TEXT(1:34)
                     MOVE  ONCP-DSTCDP0 OF KEY-DB-TABLE
                                            TO BSGDISP-TEXT(35:)
                     PERFORM  S7700-BSGDISP-RTN
                        THRU  S7700-BSGDISP-EXT
           END-EVALUATE
      *
           MOVE  SPACE                      TO   BSGDISP-TEXT
      *
           .
       S0140-KEYVALUE-DISP-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *  수행조건 : 프로그램 시작전 기본설정 및 초기화
      *  처리기능 : 사용자정보 변수 SET
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S0150-USID-INFO-SET-RTN.
      *
      *    MOVE  "S0150"                    TO   BSGEROR-PARA
      *
      *VARLEN
      *
           IF  BICOM-TRAN-START-YMS = SPACE
           THEN
               MOVE  CONT-SYSERROR  TO   DBIO-STAT
               MOVE  "S9000099"     TO   XZUGEROR-I-ERRCD
               MOVE  "UKLA0002"     TO   XZUGEROR-I-TREAT-CD
               MOVE   9902          TO   XZUGEROR-I-LINE
               MOVE
                     "BICOM-TRAN-START-YMS 미입력"
                                    TO   XZUGEROR-I-MSG
               PERFORM  S9100-ERROR-END-RTN
                  THRU  S9100-ERROR-END-EXT
           END-IF
      *
           IF  BICOM-USER-EMPID     = SPACE
           THEN
               MOVE  CONT-SYSERROR  TO   DBIO-STAT
               MOVE  "S9000099"     TO   XZUGEROR-I-ERRCD
               MOVE  "UKLA0002"     TO   XZUGEROR-I-TREAT-CD
               MOVE   9903          TO   XZUGEROR-I-LINE
               MOVE
                     "BICOM-USER-EMPID 미입력"
                                    TO   XZUGEROR-I-MSG
               PERFORM  S9100-ERROR-END-RTN
                  THRU  S9100-ERROR-END-EXT
           END-IF
      *
      *
           IF  COND-DBIO-INSERT OR COND-DBIO-UPDATE
                                OR COND-DBIO-LKUPDT
           THEN
               MOVE  DBIO-RECORD    TO   DB-TABLE
           END-IF
      *
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *    이하 프로그램은
      *    호출한 프로그램에서SET된
      *    SYS-LAST-PRCSS-YMS, SYS-LAST-UNO를
      *    변경하지 않고 INSERT를 처리한다
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *-- ZBD0500 : 배치원장 복원작업
      *-- ZBD0510 : 배치원장 반영작업
      *-- ZBD0550 : 계획정지후 본원장반영작업(업무별)
      *-- ZBD0560 : 계획정지후 본원장반영작업(테이블별)
      *---ZXXXXXX : 비상 예비용
      *
           IF DBIO-CALL-PGM-ID = "ZBD0500" OR "ZBD0510" OR
                                 "ZBD0550" OR "ZBD0560" OR
                                 "ZXXXXXX"
           THEN
              CONTINUE
           ELSE
      *
              IF  COND-DBIO-INSERT OR COND-DBIO-UPDATE
                                   OR COND-DBIO-LKUPDT
              THEN
                  MOVE  BICOM-USER-EMPID
                    TO  SYS-LAST-UNO OF DB-TABLE
                        SYS-LAST-UNO OF DBIO-RECORD
      *
                  IF    COND-DBIO-INSERT
                  THEN
                        MOVE  BICOM-TRAN-START-YMS
                          TO  SYS-LAST-PRCSS-YMS OF DB-TABLE
                              SYS-LAST-PRCSS-YMS OF DBIO-RECORD
                  END-IF
              END-IF
      *
           END-IF
           .
       S0150-USID-INFO-SET-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *
      *
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *  수행조건 : 입력정보 및 기본정보 검증
      *  처리기능 : 기본항목검증
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S0500-CHECK-RTN.
      *
           MOVE  "S0500"                    TO   BSGEROR-PARA
      *
           IF  SICOM-OPER-DSTCD             =    CONT-TEMP  OR
                                                 CONT-DAY   OR
                                                 CONT-STOP
           THEN
               CONTINUE
           ELSE
               MOVE  CONT-SYSERROR          TO   DBIO-STAT
      *{E} 정의되지 않은 거래모드입니다.(거래모드구분)
               MOVE  "S9000002"             TO   XZUGEROR-I-ERRCD
      *{E} BI거래모드구분 오류 입니다.(@1@)
               MOVE  "UKLA0002"             TO   XZUGEROR-I-TREAT-CD
               MOVE
           "정의되지 않은 거래모드입니다.(거래모드구분)"
                                            TO   XZUGEROR-I-MSG
               PERFORM  S9100-ERROR-END-RTN
                  THRU  S9100-ERROR-END-EXT
           END-IF
      *
      * DBIO-키 입력 검증
           IF  COND-DBIO-INSERT  OR
               COND-DBIO-LKUPDT  OR
               COND-DBIO-FETCH   OR
               COND-DBIO-CLOSE
           THEN
               CONTINUE
           ELSE
               IF  DBIO-KEY                 =    SPACE
               THEN
                   MOVE  CONT-SYSERROR      TO   DBIO-STAT
      *{E} DBIO-KEY 미입력 오류입니다.
                   MOVE  "S9000003"         TO   XZUGEROR-I-ERRCD
                   MOVE  "UKLA0002"         TO   XZUGEROR-I-TREAT-CD
                   MOVE   0301              TO   XZUGEROR-I-LINE
                   MOVE
           "DBIO-KEY 미입력 오류입니다."
                                            TO   XZUGEROR-I-MSG
                   PERFORM  S9100-ERROR-END-RTN
                      THRU  S9100-ERROR-END-EXT
               END-IF
           END-IF
      *
      * DBIO-FUNCTION 코드 정합성 검증
           IF      COND-DBIO-SELECT  OR  COND-DBIO-UPDATE
               OR  COND-DBIO-INSERT
               OR  COND-DBIO-DELETE  OR  COND-DBIO-DELFRC
               OR  COND-DBIO-SELFST  OR  COND-DBIO-LKUPDT
               OR  COND-DBIO-OPEN    OR  COND-DBIO-FETCH
               OR  COND-DBIO-CLOSE
           THEN
               CONTINUE
           ELSE
               MOVE  CONT-SYSERROR          TO   DBIO-STAT
      *{E} DBIO-FUNCTION코드 오류입니다.
               MOVE  "S9000001"             TO   XZUGEROR-I-ERRCD
      *{E} DBIO-FUNCTION코드 오류 입니다.(@1@)
               MOVE  "UKLA0002"             TO   XZUGEROR-I-TREAT-CD
               MOVE   0102                  TO   XZUGEROR-I-LINE
               MOVE
           "DBIO-FUNCTION코드 오류입니다."
                                            TO   XZUGEROR-I-MSG
               PERFORM  S9100-ERROR-END-RTN
                  THRU  S9100-ERROR-END-EXT
           END-IF
      *
      * DBIO-ACCESS-KEY 정합성 검증
           IF  COND-DBIO-PK
           THEN
               CONTINUE
           ELSE
               MOVE  CONT-SYSERROR          TO   DBIO-STAT
      *{E} DBIO입력항목 검증오류입니다(DBIO-ACCESS-KEY)
               MOVE  "S9000004"             TO   XZUGEROR-I-ERRCD
      *{E} DBIO-ACCESS-KEY 오류 입니다.(@1@)
               MOVE  "UKLA0002"             TO   XZUGEROR-I-TREAT-CD
               MOVE
           "DBIO입력항목 검증오류입니다(DBIO-ACCESS-KEY)"
                                            TO   XZUGEROR-I-MSG
               PERFORM  S9100-ERROR-END-RTN
                  THRU  S9100-ERROR-END-EXT
           END-IF
      *
      * DBIO-ACCESS-COND 정합성 검증
           IF  COND-DBIO-0  OR  COND-DBIO-1  OR
               COND-DBIO-2  OR  COND-DBIO-3  OR
               COND-DBIO-4
           THEN
               IF  COND-DBIO-SELFST  OR COND-DBIO-OPEN    OR
                   COND-DBIO-FETCH   OR COND-DBIO-CLOSE
               THEN
                   IF  COND-DBIO-0
                   THEN
                       MOVE  CONT-SYSERROR  TO   DBIO-STAT
      *{E} DBIO-ACCESS-COND 오류입니다
                       MOVE  "S9000005"     TO   XZUGEROR-I-ERRCD
      *{E} DBIO-ACCESS-COND 오류 입니다.(@1@)
                       MOVE  "UKLA0002"     TO   XZUGEROR-I-TREAT-CD
                       MOVE   0501          TO   XZUGEROR-I-LINE
                       MOVE
           "DBIO-ACCESS-COND 오류입니다"
                                            TO   XZUGEROR-I-MSG
                       PERFORM  S9100-ERROR-END-RTN
                          THRU  S9100-ERROR-END-EXT
                   ELSE
                       CONTINUE
                   END-IF
               ELSE
                   CONTINUE
               END-IF
           ELSE
               IF  COND-DBIO-SELECT  OR COND-DBIO-INSERT  OR
                   COND-DBIO-UPDATE  OR COND-DBIO-LKUPDT  OR
                   COND-DBIO-DELETE  OR COND-DBIO-DELFRC
               THEN
                   CONTINUE
               ELSE
                   MOVE  CONT-SYSERROR      TO   DBIO-STAT
      *{E} DBIO-ACCESS-COND 오류입니다
                   MOVE  "S9000005"         TO   XZUGEROR-I-ERRCD
      *{E} DBIO-ACCESS-COND 오류입니다.(@1@)
                   MOVE  "UKLA0002"         TO   XZUGEROR-I-TREAT-CD
                   MOVE   0502              TO   XZUGEROR-I-LINE
                   MOVE
           "DBIO-ACCESS-COND 오류입니다"
                                            TO   XZUGEROR-I-MSG
                   PERFORM  S9100-ERROR-END-RTN
                      THRU  S9100-ERROR-END-EXT
               END-IF
           END-IF
      *
      * DBIO-LOCK-YN 정합성검증
           IF  COND-DBIO-LOCK      OR
               COND-DBIO-UNLOCK
           THEN
               CONTINUE
           ELSE
      *        MOVE  "N"                    TO   DBIO-LOCK-YN
      *{E} DBIO-LOCK-YN(조건) 오류입니다
               MOVE  "S9000006"             TO   XZUGEROR-I-ERRCD
      *{E} DBIO-LOCK-YN 오류 입니다.(@1@)
               MOVE  "UKLA0002"             TO   XZUGEROR-I-TREAT-CD
               MOVE   0601                  TO   XZUGEROR-I-LINE
               MOVE
           "DBIO-LOCK-YN(조건) 오류입니다"
                                            TO   XZUGEROR-I-MSG
               PERFORM  S9100-ERROR-END-RTN
                  THRU  S9100-ERROR-END-EXT
           END-IF
      *
           IF  COND-DBIO-LOCK AND
               DBIO-ACCESS-KEY(1:2)  NOT =  CONT-PK
           THEN
      *{E} DBIO-LOCK-YN(조건) 오류입니다
               MOVE  "S9000006"             TO   XZUGEROR-I-ERRCD
      *{E} DBIO-LOCK-YN 오류 입니다.(@1@)
               MOVE  "UKLA0002"             TO   XZUGEROR-I-TREAT-CD
               MOVE   0602                  TO   XZUGEROR-I-LINE
               MOVE
           "DBIO-LOCK-YN(조건) 오류입니다"
                                            TO   XZUGEROR-I-MSG
               PERFORM  S9100-ERROR-END-RTN
                  THRU  S9100-ERROR-END-EXT
           END-IF
      *
      * 입력값의 조합검증
           IF  DBIO-ACCESS-KEY(1:2)           =    CONT-PK
           THEN
               CONTINUE
           ELSE
               IF  COND-DBIO-INSERT         OR
                   COND-DBIO-UPDATE         OR
                   COND-DBIO-DELETE         OR
                   COND-DBIO-DELFRC
               THEN
                   MOVE  CONT-SYSERROR      TO   DBIO-STAT
      *{E} DBIO-FUNCTION 또는 DBIO-ACCESS-KEY 오류입니다
                   MOVE  "S9000007"         TO   XZUGEROR-I-ERRCD
      *{E} DBIO-FUNCTION 또는 DBIO-ACCESS-KEY 오류 입니다.(@1@)
                   MOVE  "UKLA0002"         TO   XZUGEROR-I-TREAT-CD
                   MOVE
           "DBIO-FUNCTION 또는 DBIO-ACCESS-KEY 오류입니다"
                                            TO   XZUGEROR-I-MSG
                   PERFORM  S9100-ERROR-END-RTN
                      THRU  S9100-ERROR-END-EXT
               ELSE
                   CONTINUE
               END-IF
           END-IF
      *
           IF  COND-DBIO-DELETE OR COND-DBIO-DELFRC
           THEN
               IF  COND-DBIO-LOCK
               THEN
                   CONTINUE
               ELSE
                   MOVE  CONT-SYSERROR      TO   DBIO-STAT
      *{E} DBIO-LOCK-YN(조건) 오류입니다
                   MOVE  "S9000006"         TO   XZUGEROR-I-ERRCD
      *{E} DBIO-FUNCTION(@1@)시 잠금조건 오류 입니다.
                   MOVE  "UKLA0002"         TO   XZUGEROR-I-TREAT-CD
                   MOVE   0603              TO   XZUGEROR-I-LINE
                   MOVE
           "DBIO-LOCK-YN(조건) 오류입니다"
                                            TO   XZUGEROR-I-MSG
                   PERFORM  S9100-ERROR-END-RTN
                      THRU  S9100-ERROR-END-EXT
               END-IF
           ELSE
               IF  COND-DBIO-LOCK
               THEN
                   IF  COND-DBIO-OPEN       OR
                       COND-DBIO-FETCH      OR
                       COND-DBIO-SELFST
                   THEN
                       MOVE  CONT-SYSERROR  TO   DBIO-STAT
      *{E} DBIO-LOCK-YN(조건) 오류입니다
                       MOVE  "S9000006"     TO   XZUGEROR-I-ERRCD
      *{E} DBIO-FUNCTION(@1@)시 잠금조건 오류 입니다.
                       MOVE  "UKLA0002"     TO   XZUGEROR-I-TREAT-CD
                       MOVE   0604          TO   XZUGEROR-I-LINE
                       MOVE
           "DBIO-LOCK-YN(조건) 오류입니다"
                                            TO   XZUGEROR-I-MSG
                       PERFORM  S9100-ERROR-END-RTN
                          THRU  S9100-ERROR-END-EXT
                   ELSE
                       CONTINUE
                   END-IF
               ELSE
                   CONTINUE
               END-IF
           END-IF
      *
      *
      *원장갱신불가여부(여)
      *    IF  SICOM-LEDGR-UPDAT-PRHB-YN  =   "1"
      *
      *    THEN
      *        IF  COND-DBIO-LOCK AND COND-DBIO-SELECT
      *        THEN
      *            MOVE  CONT-SYSERROR  TO   DBIO-STAT
      *{E} 원장갱신불가 거래시 LOCK SELECT 불가 입니다
      *            MOVE  "S9000021"     TO   XZUGEROR-I-ERRCD
      *            MOVE  "UKLA0002"     TO   XZUGEROR-I-TREAT-CD
      *            MOVE
      *    "원장갱신불가 거래시 LOCK SELECT 불가 입니다"
      *                                 TO   XZUGEROR-I-MSG
      *            PERFORM  S9100-ERROR-END-RTN
      *               THRU  S9100-ERROR-END-EXT
      *        ELSE
      *            IF  COND-DBIO-UPDATE   OR
      *                COND-DBIO-LKUPDT
      *            THEN
      *                MOVE  CONT-SYSERROR  TO   DBIO-STAT
      *{E} 원장갱신불가 거래시 UPDATE 불가 입니다
      *                MOVE  "S9000022"     TO   XZUGEROR-I-ERRCD
      *                MOVE  "UKLA0002"     TO   XZUGEROR-I-TREAT-CD
      *                MOVE
      *    "원장갱신불가 거래시 UPDATE 불가 입니다"
      *                                     TO   XZUGEROR-I-MSG
      *                PERFORM  S9100-ERROR-END-RTN
      *                   THRU  S9100-ERROR-END-EXT
      *            END-IF
      *        END-IF
      *    END-IF
      *
           IF  COND-DBIO-SELECT  OR COND-DBIO-INSERT  OR
               COND-DBIO-UPDATE  OR
               COND-DBIO-DELETE  OR COND-DBIO-DELFRC  OR
               COND-DBIO-SELFST  OR COND-DBIO-OPEN
           THEN
               PERFORM  S0510-IN-CHECK-RTN THRU S0510-IN-CHECK-EXT
           ELSE
               CONTINUE
           END-IF
           .
       S0500-CHECK-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *  수행조건 : DBIO-키 값 검증
      *  처리기능 : DBIO-키 값에 NULL 입력시 에러처리
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S0510-IN-CHECK-RTN.
      *
           MOVE  "S0510"                    TO   BSGEROR-PARA
      *
           EVALUATE  TRUE
               WHEN  COND-DBIO-PK
                     IF  GROUP-CO-CDP0  =  SPACE
                     THEN
                         MOVE  "COL-NM: GROUP-CO-CD"
                           TO   BSGDISP-TEXT
                         PERFORM  S0511-ERROR-SET-RTN
                            THRU  S0511-ERROR-SET-EXT
                     ELSE
                         CONTINUE
                     END-IF
                     IF  BASE-YMP0  =  SPACE
                     THEN
                         MOVE  "COL-NM: BASE-YM"
                           TO   BSGDISP-TEXT
                         PERFORM  S0511-ERROR-SET-RTN
                            THRU  S0511-ERROR-SET-EXT
                     ELSE
                         CONTINUE
                     END-IF
                     IF  ONCP-DSTCDP0  =  SPACE
                     THEN
                         MOVE  "COL-NM: ONCP-DSTCD"
                           TO   BSGDISP-TEXT
                         PERFORM  S0511-ERROR-SET-RTN
                            THRU  S0511-ERROR-SET-EXT
                     ELSE
                         CONTINUE
                     END-IF
                     IF  1 < DBIO-ACCESS-COND
                     THEN
                         PERFORM  S0512-ERROR-SET-RTN
                            THRU  S0512-ERROR-SET-EXT
                     END-IF
           END-EVALUATE
      *

           .
       S0510-IN-CHECK-EXT.
           EXIT.

      *
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *  수행조건 : DBIO-키 값 검증
      *  처리기능 : DBIO-키 값에 NULL 입력시 에러처리
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S0511-ERROR-SET-RTN.

      *    MOVE  "S0511"                    TO   BSGEROR-PARA

           MOVE  CONT-SYSERROR              TO   DBIO-STAT
           MOVE  "S9000003"                 TO   XZUGEROR-I-ERRCD
           MOVE  "UKLA0002"                 TO   XZUGEROR-I-TREAT-CD
           MOVE   0302                      TO   XZUGEROR-I-LINE
           MOVE
           "DBIO-KEY 미입력 오류입니다."
                                            TO   XZUGEROR-I-MSG
           PERFORM  S9100-ERROR-END-RTN
              THRU  S9100-ERROR-END-EXT
           .
       S0511-ERROR-SET-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *  수행조건 : DBIO-ACCESS-COND 값 검증
      *  처리기능 : DBIO-ACCESS-COND 값이 > 설정값 에러처리
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S0512-ERROR-SET-RTN.

      *    MOVE  "S0512"                    TO   BSGEROR-PARA

           MOVE  CONT-SYSERROR              TO   DBIO-STAT
      *{E} DBIO-ACCESS-COND 오류입니다
           MOVE  "S9000005"                 TO   XZUGEROR-I-ERRCD
      *{E} DBIO-ACCESS-COND 오류 입니다.(@1@)
           MOVE  "UKLA0002"                 TO   XZUGEROR-I-TREAT-CD
           MOVE   0503                      TO   XZUGEROR-I-LINE
           MOVE
           "DBIO-ACCESS-COND(MAX) 오류입니다"
                                            TO   XZUGEROR-I-MSG

           MOVE
           "BPG/DBIO/시작조건적용최대컬럼갯수 항목을 설정하세요"
                                            TO   BSGDISP-TEXT
           PERFORM  S9100-ERROR-END-RTN
              THRU  S9100-ERROR-END-EXT
           .
       S0512-ERROR-SET-EXT.
           EXIT.

      *
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *  수행조건 : DBIO-FUNCTION 구분이 SELECT일때 실행된다.
      *  처리기능 : DBIO-ACCESS-KEY와 DBIO-LOCK-YN에따라
      *             다른 조건으로 SELECT를 한다.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S1000-SELECT-RTN.
      *
           MOVE  "S1000"                    TO   BSGEROR-PARA
      *
           IF  DBIO-LOCK-YN                 =    CONT-Y
           THEN
               PERFORM  S8710-SEL-LOCK-RTN   THRU S8710-SEL-LOCK-EXT
           ELSE
               EVALUATE  TRUE
                   WHEN  COND-DBIO-PK
                         PERFORM  S8720-SEL-NOLOCK0-RTN
                            THRU  S8720-SEL-NOLOCK0-EXT
               END-EVALUATE

           END-IF
           .
       S1000-SELECT-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *  수행조건 : DBIO-FUNCTION이 SELFST 일때 실행한다
      *  처리기능 : 조건에 해당하는 첫번째 ROW를 RETURN 한다
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S2000-SELFST-RTN.
      *
