       S8110-DECLARE-KEY0-RTN.
           EXEC SQL DECLARE CUR_MODE_KEY0 CURSOR FOR
␀␀␀␀␀␀     SELECT                                                       ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀
                  "그룹회사코드",
                  "기준년월",
                  "자기자본구분",
