                  "등록직원번호",
                  "등록년월일",
                  "시스템최종처리일시",
                  "시스템최종사용자번호"
             FROM DB2DBA.THKJL0049
␀␀␀␀␀␀      WHERE ( 'PK' = :WORK-ACCECODE AND 1 <= :WORK-ACCESS-COND    ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀
␀␀␀␀␀␀        AND "그룹회사코드" = :GROUP-CO-CDP0                     ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀
␀␀␀␀␀␀        AND "기준년월" = :BASE-YMP0                             ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀
␀␀␀␀␀␀        AND "자기자본구분" >= :ONCP-DSTCDP0 )                   ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀
␀␀␀␀␀␀      ORDER BY                                                    ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀
␀␀␀␀␀␀            "그룹회사코드" ASC                                  ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀
␀␀␀␀␀␀           ,"기준년월" ASC                                      ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀
␀␀␀␀␀␀           ,"자기자본구분" ASC                                  ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀
␀␀␀␀␀␀     END-EXEC                                                     ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀
␀␀␀␀␀␀*                                                                 ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀
␀␀␀␀␀␀     IF  SQLCODE                      =    ZERO                   ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀
␀␀␀␀␀␀     THEN                                                         ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀
␀␀␀␀␀␀         CONTINUE                                                 ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀
␀␀␀␀␀␀     ELSE                                                         ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀
␀␀␀␀␀␀         MOVE  CONT-SQLER            TO   DBIO-STAT               ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀
␀␀␀␀␀␀         PERFORM  S9100-ERROR-END-RTN                             ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀
␀␀␀␀␀␀            THRU  S9100-ERROR-END-EXT                             ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀
␀␀␀␀␀␀     END-IF                                                       ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀
␀␀␀␀␀␀*                                                                 ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀
           EXEC SQL OPEN  CUR_MODE_KEY0 END-EXEC
␀␀␀␀␀␀*                                                                 ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀
␀␀␀␀␀␀     IF  SQLCODE                      =    -502                   ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀
␀␀␀␀␀␀     THEN                                                         ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀
               EXEC SQL CLOSE  CUR_MODE_KEY0 END-EXEC
