      *              MOVE  "D9900803"       TO   XZUGEROR-I-ERRCD
               WHEN  OTHER
                     IF  DBIO-SQLCODE(4:1) = "9" OR DBIO-SQLCODE = -805
                     THEN
                         MOVE CONT-SYSERROR TO   DBIO-STAT
                     ELSE
                         MOVE CONT-SQLER    TO   DBIO-STAT
                     END-IF
      *{E} DBIO SQL 에러입니다
                     MOVE  "D9900000"       TO   XZUGEROR-I-ERRCD
                     MOVE  XZUGEROR-I-SQL-CD(2:)
                                            TO   XZUGEROR-I-ERRCD(4:)
                     MOVE  "UKLA0002"       TO   XZUGEROR-I-TREAT-CD
                     MOVE
           " DBIO SQL 에러입니다"
                                            TO   XZUGEROR-I-MSG
           END-EVALUATE
      *
           IF  XZUGEROR-I-TREAT-CD          =    "UKLA9999"
           THEN
               MOVE  "DBIO    "             TO   XZUGEROR-I-PGM-ID
           ELSE
      *        MOVE  DBIO-CALL-PGM-ID       TO   XZUGEROR-I-PGM-ID
               MOVE  CONT-PROGRAM-ID        TO   XZUGEROR-I-PGM-ID
           END-IF
      *
           IF  XZUGEROR-I-ERRCD         =    SPACE
           THEN
      *{E} DBIO모듈에서 에러종료 되었습니다.
               MOVE  "S9000017"             TO   XZUGEROR-I-ERRCD
                     MOVE
           "DBIO모듈에서에러종료되었습니다"
                                            TO   XZUGEROR-I-MSG
           ELSE
               CONTINUE
           END-IF
      *
