               COND-DBIO-MRNF
           THEN
               MOVE  CONT-N                 TO   WORK-ERR-SET-YN
      *        MOVE "결과코드{01}과{02}는에러처리를하지않습니다."
           ELSE
               CONTINUE
           END-IF
      *
           IF  COMM-DB-II-OUTPT-DSTCD            =    "1" OR "9"
           THEN
               PERFORM  S7900-BSGTRCE-RTN THRU S7900-BSGTRCE-EXT
               IF  WORK-ERR-SET-YN = CONT-Y
               THEN
                   MOVE  XZUGEROR-I-MSG     TO   BSGDISP-TEXT
