      *        PERFORM  S8900-COLUMN-DISPLAY-RTN
      *           THRU  S8900-COLUMN-DISPLAY-EXT
      *    END-IF

      *
           MOVE  DBIO-STAT                  TO   XZUGEROR-I-STAT
